msgstr "Zaženi &kget; (morali bi videti Opusti cilj)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag and drop the required &URL; in the &kget; window/Drop Target."
msgstr "Povlecite in spustite potreben &URL; v &kget; okno/Spustno Tarčo."

