#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kget; Drop Target"
msgstr "&kget; Opusti cilj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kget; Drop Target has four options."
msgstr "&kget; Opusti cilj ima štiri možnosti."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Screenshot of &kget; drop target</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kget; opusti cilj</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Screenshot of &kget; drop target</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kget; opusti cilj</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kget; Drop Target options"
msgstr "&kget; opusti možnosti cilja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:94
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right click on the drop target to see the options."
msgstr "Z desnim klikom na opusti cilj se bodo prikazale možnosti."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Start / Resume All</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenuitem>Začni / Nadaljuj Vse</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start a download or resume all the pending downloads. The shortcut for "
"doing this is <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"Da pričnete z prenosom ali da nadaljujete z vsemi. Bližnjica za to je "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>R</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show/Hide Main Window"
msgstr "Prikaži/Skrij Glavno Okno"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "This option shows or minimizes the main window to the system tray."
msgstr "Ta možnost vam prikaže ali skrije glavno okno v sistemsko vrstico."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sticky"
msgstr "Prilepi"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Makes the &kget; drop target undraggable."
msgstr "Spustne tarče se ne bo dalo premikati."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quit &kget;"
msgstr "Zapri &kget;"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:148 index.docbook:698
#, no-c-format
msgid "Quits &kget;"
msgstr "Zapre &kget;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kget;'s Configuration window"
msgstr "Konfiguracijsko okno &kget;-a"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:160
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kget;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kget;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opens the &kget; configuration window"
msgstr "Odpre &kget;-ovo okno za konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Appearance</title>"
msgstr "<title>Videz</title>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:172
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Appearance</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Videz</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Appearance</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Videz</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenuitem>Appearance</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenuitem>Videz</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can modify the various appearance related stuff here."
msgstr "Tukaj lahko spremenite različne stvari, povezane z videzom."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use Drop Target"
msgstr "Uporabi Opusti cilj"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid "Uncheck this if you do not want the &kget; Drop Target."
msgstr "Odstranite kljukico, če ne želite &kget; Opusti cilj."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable animations"
msgstr "Omogoči animacije"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enables few fancy animations."
msgstr "Omogoči nekaj animacij."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Groups"
msgstr "Skupine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can group downloads."
msgstr "Prenose lahko razdelite v skupine."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Groups</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Skupine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Groups</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Skupine</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use default folders for groups as suggestion"
msgstr "Kot predlog uporabite privzete mape za skupine"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tick this box if you want &kget; to use default folders for your downloads."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da &kget; za svoje prenose uporablja privzete "
"mape."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:258
#, no-c-format
msgid "Network"
msgstr "Omrežnje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can modify your network related settings here."
msgstr "Tu lahko prilagodite nastavitve v zvezi z omrežjem."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:261
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Network</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Omrežje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Network</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Omrežje</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limit Maximum Downloads Per Group"
msgstr "Omeji Največje Število Prenosov Na Skupino"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want Download limits to be implemented."
msgstr "Označite to polje, če želite, da se Omejevanje prenosov izvaja."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:288
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed Limit"
msgstr "Omejitev Hitrosti"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Check this box if you want the Global speed limits to be used."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da se uporablja Globalne omejitve hitrosti."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global download limit"
msgstr "Omejitev globalnih prenosov"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:306
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum global download limit."
msgstr "Nastavi mejo za največji globalni prenos."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:314
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global upload limit"
msgstr "Omejitev globalnega nalaganja"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum upload limit."
msgstr "Nastavi mejo za največje nalaganje."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid "Reconnect on Broken Connection"
msgstr "Ob Prekinjeni Povezavi se Ponovno Poveži"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box if you want &kget; to reconnect after an error or a broken "
"connection."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, če želite, da se &kget; ponovno poveže po napaki ali "
"prekinjeni povezavi."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number of retries"
msgstr "Število ponovnih poskusov"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the maximum number of time &kget; will try to reconnect."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite največje število ponovnih poskusov, ko se bo &kget; poskušal "
"ponovno povezati."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:353
#, no-c-format
msgid "Retry after"
msgstr "Poskusi ponovno po"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:358
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set the retrying interval here (in seconds)"
msgstr "Nastavi interval (v sekundah) za ponovni poskus"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid "Web Interface"
msgstr "Spletni Vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:369
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enable the web interface, check <guilabel>Enable Web Interface</"
"guilabel>; default port is 8080, and you configure any port higher than "
"1024. Then set <guilabel>User</guilabel> and <guilabel>Password</guilabel>. "
"You can access your web interface at http://127.0.0.1:&lt;port&gt;. You will "
"need to enter the username and password to get access."
msgstr ""
"Da omogočite spletni vmesnik, označite <guilabel>Omogoči Spletni Vmesnik</"
"guilabel>; privzeta vrata so 8080, vi pa konfigurirajte katera koli vrata, "
"višja od 1024. Nato nastavite <guilabel>Uporabnik</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Geslo</guilabel>. Do spletnega vmesnika lahko dostopate na "
"http://127.0.0.1:&lt;port&gt;. Vnesti boste morali uporabniško ime in geslo, "
"da si zagotovite dostop."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:377
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Web Interface</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Spletni Vmesnik</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Web Interface</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Spletni Vmesnik</phrase>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verification"
msgstr "Preverjanje"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:392
#, no-c-format
msgid "Verify your downloads."
msgstr "Preverite vaše prenose."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Verification</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Preverjanje</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:400
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Verification</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Preverjanje</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:405
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using the two methods <guilabel>Automatic checksums verification</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Signature</guilabel> you can verify your downloads. You just "
"have to tick the <guilabel>Automatic verification</guilabel> check box."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo dveh načinov <guilabel>Samodejno preverjanje kontrolne vsote</"
"guilabel> in <guilabel>Podpis</guilabel> lahko preverite vaše prenose. Samo "
"odkljukajte polje <guilabel>Samodejno preverjanje</guilabel>"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:410
#, no-c-format
msgid "Integration"
msgstr "Integracija"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use as download manager for Konqueror"
msgstr "Uporaba kot upravljalnik prenosov za Konqueror"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can set &kget; as your download manager for &konqueror;."
msgstr "&kget; lahko nastavite kot vaš upravljalnik prenosov za &konqueror;."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid "Monitor clipboard for files to download"
msgstr "Spremljaj odložišče za datoteke, ki jih je potrebno prenesti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can turn on this feature that asks if you want to download &URL;s copied "
"into the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Vklopite lahko funkcijo, ki vpraša, če želite prenesti &URL;-je, ki so "
"skopirani v odložišču."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Napredno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:442
#, no-c-format
msgid "Modify Advanced Options."
msgstr "Spremeni Napredne nastavitve."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:444
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Advanced Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Napredne Nastavitve</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:450
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Advanced Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Napredne Nastavitve</phrase>"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:459
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable system tray icon"
msgstr "Omogoči ikono v sistemski vrstici"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:464
#, no-c-format
msgid "This check box enables the &kget; system tray icon."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, da boste imeli &kget;-ovo ikono v sistemski vrstici."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute action after all downloads have been finished"
msgstr "Izvrši dejanje po koncu vseh prenosov"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box to enable Quitting &kget; after all downloads have finished. "
"At startup you can choose to Restore Download state. Such as Stop All "
"downloads/ Start All downloads."
msgstr ""
"Označite to polje, da omogočite Izhod iz &kget;-a po končanih vseh prenosih. "
"Na začetku lahko izberete Obnovi Stanje Prenosa. Prav tako lahko izberete "
"Ustavi Vse prenose/ Začni Vse prenose."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:486
#, no-c-format
msgid "History backend"
msgstr "Zaledje zgodovine"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can choose your history backend as Sqlite or Xml."
msgstr "Za zaledje zgodovine lahko izbirate med Sqlite ali Xml."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: index.docbook:499
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable &kde; global progress tracking"
msgstr "Omogoči &kde;-jev globalni sledilnik napredka"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:504
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set &kget; to show every single download or show overall progress."
msgstr ""
"&kget; lahko nastavite, da bo prikazal vsak prenos ali splošni napredek."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plugins"
msgstr "Vtičniki"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:514
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kget; Plugins Options</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kget; Možnosti Vtičnikov</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:520
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kget; Plugins Options</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kget; Možnosti Vtičnikov</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:524
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this page you can select the transfer plugins to be used. Use the "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"pluginsettings.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject> button to change the "
"default settings for a plugin."
msgstr ""
"Na tej strani lahko izberete vtičnike za prenos, ki bodo uporabljeni. "
"Uporabite gumb <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"pluginsettings.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject>, "
"da spremenite privzete nastavitve za vtičnik."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:532
#, no-c-format
msgid "Main Window"
msgstr "Glavno Okno"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Overview of &kget;'s Main Window"
msgstr "Pregled &kget;-ovega Glavnega Okna"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "The File Menu"
msgstr "Meni Datoteka"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>New Download...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nov prenos...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add a new file to download"
msgstr "Dodaj novo datoteko za prenos"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Links...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>L</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi Povezave...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:570
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Import Links</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Uvozi Povezavo</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Import Links</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Uvozi povezavo</phrase>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:580
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This action brings up another window, where you can see and manipulate which "
"file to download. Also you can make a selection based on <guilabel>Videos</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Images</guilabel>, <guilabel>Audio</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Archives</guilabel>. There is also a text box to filter out "
"results."
msgstr ""
"To dejanje odpre novo okno, kjer lahko vidite in upravljate, katero datoteko "
"želite prenesti. Prav tako lahko ustvarite izbor glede na <guilabel>Videji</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Slike</guilabel>, <guilabel>Avdio</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Arhivi</guilabel>. Zraven je besedilno polje, da lahko filtrirate "
"rezultate."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>File</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Import Transfers...</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi Prenose...</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loads a <filename class=\"extension\">*.kgt</filename>, <filename class="
"\"extension\">*.metalink</filename>, <filename class=\"extension\">*.meta4</"
"filename> or <filename class=\"extension\">*.torrent</filename> file."
msgstr ""
"Naloži <filename class=\"extension\">*.kgt</filename>, <filename class="
